DENGUE - BRAZIL (MANAUS)
************************
A ProMED-mail post
See Also
Dengue - Brazil 980214215947
Dengue - Brazil (02) 980216185309
Dengue - Brazil (03) 980321031942
Dengue - Brazil (Belo Horizonte) 980327233449
Dengue - Brazil (Minas Gerais) 980402222750
Dengue - Brazil (Rio de Janeiro) 980326230037
Date: Thu, 02 Apr 1998 16:28:52 +0000
From: Roberts, Donald R. <droberts@mx3.usuhs.mil>

I talked to Dr. Wilson Alecrim, Director of the Instituto de Medicina
Tropical of Manaus, this morning. He told me that an epidemic of dengue
fever started in Manaus last weekend and they have already seen 240 cases
this week.
